title: 02/14/22 Hour 2 Tony Boselli & Ryan Clark
itunes:title: 02/14/22 Hour 2 Tony Boselli & Ryan Clark
description:
In hour 2, Tony Boselli joins to talk the honors of being inducted to Hall Of Fame. Ryan Clark also joins the show to give his take on the "Best Half Time Show Ever". While also stating his concern for the Bengals O-line moving forward and the roll they played in the Bengals losing efforts.
